      <title>八木飓风过后，越南首都和电子中心面临洪水风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/vietnam-capital-electronics-hub-face-flood-risk-in-yagi-s-wake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[超强台风“八木”在越南造成数十人死亡，引发的洪水正在威胁越南北部地区，包括首都河内]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/vietnam-capital-electronics-hub-face-flood-risk-in-yagi-s-wake</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 02:36:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
